<subSubSection id="4BE74DEB4C72FF85FED9FA036BFFF978" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="03421E604C72FF85FED9FA036BFFF978" blockId="20.[264,1323,1505,1732]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">
<emphasis id="3189C2724C72FF85FED9FA036E0AFA47" bold="true" box="[264,378,1505,1531]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Remarks</emphasis>
: This is one of a group of similar species close to 
<taxonomicName id="C4FD65E34C72FF85FC05FA006B87FA40" authority="Loew, 1873" authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1873" box="[980,1271,1506,1532]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Bombylius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="modestus">
<emphasis id="3189C2724C72FF85FC05FA006B13FA47" box="[980,1123,1506,1531]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">B. modestus</emphasis>
Loew, 
<number id="B5350C474C72FF85FB6DFA006B87FA40" box="[1212,1271,1506,1532]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="1873.0">1873</number>
</taxonomicName>
that are found in southern Arabia and northeastern Africa. They are keyed, described, and the male genitalia illustrated in Greathead (
<number id="B5350C474C72FF85FD09F9D06C67F9F0" box="[728,791,1586,1612]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="1967.0">1967</number>
); but note that nomenclatural errors owing to application of the name 
<taxonomicName id="C4FD65E34C72FF85FDF4F9B86DA6F9CF" box="[549,726,1626,1651]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Bombylius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="phaeopterus">
<emphasis id="3189C2724C72FF85FDF4F9B86DA6F9CF" box="[549,726,1626,1651]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">B. phaeopterus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to a common Eritrean coastal species (renamed 
<taxonomicName id="C4FD65E34C72FF85FAC0F9B86D7BF920" authority="Bowden" authorityName="Bowden" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Bombylius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="modestoides">
<emphasis id="3189C2724C72FF85FAC0F9B86EE9F927" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">B. modestoides</emphasis>
Bowden
</taxonomicName>
) rather than the southern Ethiopian species designated in Bezzi (
<number id="B5350C474C72FF85FEC0F9486E20F978" box="[273,336,1706,1732]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="1924.0">1924</number>
; syn. 
<taxonomicName id="C4FD65E34C72FF85FE42F9486D99F978" authority="Greathead" authorityName="Greathead" box="[403,745,1706,1732]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Bombylius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="phaeopteroides">
<emphasis id="3189C2724C72FF85FE42F9486D18F97F" box="[403,616,1706,1731]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">B. phaeopteroides</emphasis>
Greathead
</taxonomicName>
) were corrected by Bowden (
<number id="B5350C474C72FF85FB92F9486BF3F978" box="[1091,1155,1706,1732]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21" value="1975.0">1975</number>
).
</paragraph>
